document_data.mainbody:
he Garblueth family was a Amnian family during the 14 century DR.
Lord Garblueth died in 1366 DR, and his sole heir was his daughter Faerthae Garblueth, who bequeathed her family fortune to the Church of Waukeen.
* Lord Garblueth of Athkatla.
* Fury Faerthae Garblueth, a priest at Goldspires.
